{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/About.gif?t=1726816560\" /><br>\u2220 Prepare for an adrenaline-pumping and immersive VR experience that combines fast-paced combat and strategic rune drawing inspired by Slavic mythology. The fate of the sanctuary and the whole world, is in your hands<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/Shooter.gif?t=1726816560\" /><br>\u2220 Plunge into the world of Slavic mythology and take on the role of a brave shaman in this immersive roguelike VR Wave Shooter. Defend the holy shrine of the god &quot;Veles&quot; from relentless waves of monstrous creatures summoned by the powerful rival &quot;Perun&quot; in easy to pick up but hard to master short gaming sessions<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/Cin_Title_no_RB_New.gif?t=1726816560\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/BecomeExpert.gif?t=1726816560\" /><br>\u2220 Your shamanic body may be frail, but your bending powers are not. Armed with the power of ancient runes master the elements of nature fire, water, earth and air<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/Cin_Enemies_New.gif?t=1726816560\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/MasterRunes.gif?t=1726816560\" /><br>\u2220 Draw various runes with an intuitive spellcasting system using the elemental Runepads. <br>Cast powerful spells by solely moving your hands<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/Cin_Runepad_New.gif?t=1726816560\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/ElementalSpells.gif?t=1726816560\" /><br>\u2220 Discover and master 16 different elemental spells.  <br>Use them against Perun's dark creatures to exploit their weaknesses <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/Cin_Bolts_New.gif?t=1726816560\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/Cin_Beam_New.gif?t=1726816560\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/Roguelike.gif?t=1726816560\" /><br>\u2220 Start your run with basic elemental magic and unlock new powerful spells. Upgrade any spell according to your playstyle, adding even more variety to your runs<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/Cin_Upgrades.gif?t=1726816560\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/SlavicMythology.gif?t=1726816560\" /><br>\u2220 Use your abilities against slavic mythological creatures. The stronger the waves, the greater the challenges that require quick thinking and strategic decisions but remember that each death is temporary since each run makes you more skilled<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/Cin_Restart_New.gif?t=1726816560\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/Features.gif?t=1726816560\" /><br><br>\u2022 Shamanic:          \u2022 Learn to bend elemental magic like: fire, water, earth, air<br>\u2022 Runes:                \u2022 Unlock during your run up to 16 spells<br>\u2022 Dynamic Builds: \u2022 With over 20 different upgrades to choose from throughout a run, no two attempts will ever be the same<br>\u2022 Waves:               \u2022 Learn the weaknesses of the slavic creatures and use the right spells during 15 Waves in Story Mode<br>\u2022 Pick Up &amp; Play:  \u2022 Easy to pick up but hard to master short gaming sessions<br>\u2022 Your Playstyle:   \u2022 You choose wether to focus on your reflex, timing or strategic skills<br>\u2022 Endless Mode:   \u2022 Proof your skills in the ultimate runebending test and climb up the leaderboard<br><br>Are you ready to join this epic battle and determine the fate of the world?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/Shaman_only.gif?t=1726816560\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/BMWE_Fz_2017_Web_en.gif?t=1726816560\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Beginning of Infinity","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2387750/d2b0b65a61939c1335dd33f6ff412afa777ba389.jpg"},{"name":"Storyteller","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2387750/501fb97885a54d2787fd09690ed66bd1fe29e00b.jpg"},{"name":"Almost die","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2387750/c3daad61d62f92a369bb0aec97aa65f07c3bc18d.jpg"},{"name":"I think my Stick is stuck","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2387750/818892194507149e4794f98f2fc0e186b6ff9637.jpg"},{"name":"Master of the Elements","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2387750/03d4df2f5e94c95d3e3760695e7ffbad88ab3eaa.jpg"},{"name":"Finish with most useless Element","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2387750/068d42ba7b94c130bc695fa839337106c77ecd28.jpg"},{"name":"Healer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2387750/c99b2e4f5f2848e